name: Carnival Conor Crown
description:
This handmade crown is prefect for your little one. All my items are made with the upmost attention to detail and care. Crowns are adjustable and have a non-slip grip lining. My crowns are prefect birthday's, photo props, halloween, and just for fun! 

Please make sure to make a note to seller with the initial needed for this crown. Do not see what you want, just let me know, I love custom orders!

All my crowns are made to order, so please note there is a 7-10 business day production time. I mail every Tuesday and Thursday. If you are needing your crown by a specific date please reach out to me via convo before placing your order to make sure I can accommodate.

Please note crown may contain small parts, not recommended for under 3 without adult supervision. 

Thanks so much for checking out True Love Found!
Amy
